# LivePlotDock - Streaming Metric Chart Renderer

LivePlotDock turns numeric data streams into animated line charts for live monitoring or visual demos.

## Features
- Real-time scrolling  
- Built with Matplotlib  
- Simple CLI launch  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_LivePlotDock.git
cd 22_LivePlotDock
python visualize.py
